title: WarpGate_Official - ❓｜galxe-quest-faq

Q: **Why my Metamask Wallet is showing unsupported? **
Ans: Please temporary disable any other wallet extention; specially EVM wallet extention and refresh the page.

title: WarpGate_Official - ❓｜galxe-quest-faq
html:
**Q: Why is my Spartans Guild tasks aren't being verified on Galxe?**
Ans: We understand you may be experiencing issues with your on-chain transaction. This is likely due to high activity and congestion on the MOVE Testnet blockchain, which can affect transaction times. 

We recommend trying again or waiting a few moments before attempting the galxe task verification once more. Thank you for your patience and understanding.😊

Don’t forget to keep inviting more friends to join the WarpGate x Movement Galxe quest! 🎉

title: WarpGate_Official - ❓｜galxe-quest-faq
html:
The Parthenon site has been marking a Quest completed on our site if the *tasks* are done in Galxe rather than if the quest has been *claimed* in Galxe. Subtle difference but we need to get it corrected for the next cool things coming.

The bad news is that for some of you, it may *appear* that you have lost credit for come Quests. However, **all your work and progress is safe!**

**Here's what ya need to do:**
1️⃣ Look for Quests that say **"Pending Claim"** in the upper right-hand corner
2️⃣ **Click** on that Quest to go to it's page in Galxe
3️⃣ **Claim the quest** in Galxe
4️⃣** Refresh your Quest section** on the Parthenon Site. Your Quest should be green again.

**MAKE QUESTS GREEN AGAIN!**
